&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;â€¢&lt;/em&gt; accessing the global copy of the data&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;â€¢&lt;/em&gt; invocation of transformers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;â€¢&lt;/em&gt; APIs to enable the communication across different ASIL levels&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;â€¢&lt;/em&gt; APIs to enable the communication between Software Clusters&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;via RTE Implementation Plug-Ins outside the RTE Generator. This includes port based communication as well as Inter Runnable Variables.&lt;/p&gt;
